English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dragleave_event\"><code>dragleave</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dragover_event\"><code>dragover</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dragstart_event\"><code>dragstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/drop_event\"><code>drop</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/gotpointercapture_event\"><code>gotpointercapture</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/input_event\"><code>input</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/lostpointercapture_event\"><code>lostpointercapture</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/mscandidatewindowhide_event\"><code>mscandidatewindowhide</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/mscandidatewindowshow_event\"><code>mscandidatewindowshow</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/mscandidatewindowupdate_event\"><code>mscandidatewindowupdate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/paste_event\"><code>paste</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n </div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Atrybut <strong>dir</strong> ustawia lub pobiera kierunek pisania tekstu dla zawartości bieżącego elementu.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia_i_warto.c5.9bci","title":"Składnia i wartości","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <var>bieżącyKierunekPisania</var> = elementNodeReference.dir;\nelementNodeReference.dir = <var>nowyKierunekPisania</var>;\n</pre>\n<p><var>bieżącyKierunekPisania</var> jest łańcuchem reprezentującym kierunek pisania tekstu bieżącego elementu. <var>nowyKierunekPisania</var> to zmienna łańcuchowa, której wartość reprezentuje kierunek pisania tekstu.</p>\n<p>Możliwe wartości <strong>dir</strong> to <code>ltr</code> dla \"od lewej do prawej\" i <code>rtl</code> dla \"od prawej do lewej\".</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad","title":"Przykład","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> parg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"para1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nparg<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dir <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"rtl\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// zmienia kierunek tekstu w paragrafie \"para1\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"uwagi","title":"Uwagi","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Kierunek pisania tekstu elementu oznacza kierunek, w którym idzie tekst (do obsługi różnych języków). Języki arabski i hebrajski to typowe przykłady użycia kierunku <em>rtl</em>.</p>\n<p>Obrazek może mieć atrybut <em>dir</em> ustawiony na <em>rtl</em>. W takim wypadku atrybuty <em>title</em> i <em>alt</em> będą sformatowane i wyświetlona jako <em>rtl</em>.</p>\n<p>Jeśli tabela ma kierunek <em>rtl</em>, kolumny porządkowane są od prawej do lewej.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-HTML/html.html#ID-52460740\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C DOM Level 2 HTML: dir</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Podsumowanie","id":"podsumowanie"},{"text":"Składnia i wartości","id":"sk.c5.82adnia_i_warto.c5.9bci"},{"text":"Przykład","id":"przyk.c5.82ad"},{"text":"Uwagi","id":"uwagi"},{"text":"Specyfikacja","id":"specyfikacja"}],"summary":"Atrybut dir ustawia lub pobiera kierunek pisania tekstu dla zawartości bieżącego elementu.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLElement.dir","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLElement.dir","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLElement.dir","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTMLElement.dir","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/htmlelement/dir","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/htmlelement/dir/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement","title":"HTMLElement"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dir","title":"element.dir"}],"pageTitle":"element.dir - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}